## ūüĒó GITHUB-FIRST PROTOCOL (MANDATORY)
Before ANY code change, you MUST verify GitHub state:

1. **Pre-Session**: `git fetch origin --prune && git status` ‚ÄĒ confirm branch is synced with remote.
